{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSURL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSURL"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"url","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The URL to process.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"url"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"YES if the URL was handled by Pushwoosh, NO otherwise."}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Handles special Pushwoosh URLs, primarily used for:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Test device registration"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Register device for push testing via QR code"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Deep link tracking"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Process tracked deep links from push notifications"}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Should be called from your app’s URL handling methods. Returns YES if the URL"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"was a Pushwoosh URL and was handled, NO if it should be processed by your app."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Example","level":2,"anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Handle URLs in SceneDelegate (iOS 13+):","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["class SceneDelegate: UIResponder, UIWindowSceneDelegate {","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, openURLContexts URLContexts: Set<UIOpenURLContext>) {","        guard let url = URLContexts.first?.url else { return }","","        \/\/ First, check if Pushwoosh handles this URL","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            Logger.info(\"URL handled by Pushwoosh\")","            return","        }","","        \/\/ Handle other deep links","        DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","","    func scene(_ scene: UIScene, continue userActivity: NSUserActivity) {","        guard userActivity.activityType == NSUserActivityTypeBrowsingWeb,","              let url = userActivity.webpageURL else { return }","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return","        }","","        UniversalLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}","","\/\/ Legacy AppDelegate support","class AppDelegate: UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ app: UIApplication,","                    open url: URL,","                    options: [UIApplication.OpenURLOptionsKey: Any] = [:]) -> Bool {","","        if Pushwoosh.configure.handleOpenURL(url) {","            return true","        }","","        return DeepLinkRouter.shared.handle(url)","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handleopenurl:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Processes deep link URLs for Pushwoosh SDK functionality."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handleOpenURL:"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","title":"handleOpenURL:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handleOpenURL:","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"title":"PWConfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"role":"collection","title":"PushwooshCore","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/handleOpenURL:":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Processes deep link URLs for Pushwoosh SDK functionality."}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handleOpenURL:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handleOpenURL:","title":"handleOpenURL:","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handleopenurl:","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"handleOpenURL:"}]}}}